What's going on, Raj?

00:15.450 --> 00:17.495
Well, how would
you guys feel

00:17.539 --> 00:19.410
about going to India
for my wedding?

00:19.454 --> 00:21.978
Oh, that's so exciting!

00:22.022 --> 00:24.285
Penny, you will never guess
what I have planned

00:24.328 --> 00:27.114
