that you feed them peanuts.

00:36.427 --> 00:38.734
Are you really gonna plan
a wedding in three months?

00:38.777 --> 00:41.128
Yeah, well, her family's
doing most of the work.

00:41.171 --> 00:43.521
They're amazing.
We talk all the time.

00:43.565 --> 00:44.566
Why?

00:44.609 --> 00:46.437
Because we're
about to get married

00:46.481 --> 00:48.483
and they're gonna be my family.

00:48.526 --> 00:51.834
