I never talk to her family.

00:51.877 --> 00:53.444
Really? My parents
love Leonard.

00:53.488 --> 00:55.446
Yeah. And my mom loves
Penny, which is weird,

00:55.490 --> 00:58.188
because I never
knew she could love.

00:59.363 --> 01:01.539
And my dad has grown
to really...

01:01.583 --> 01:03.454
like Howard.

01:04.673 --> 01:08.024
Yeah, there's a nice...
coolness between us.

01:08.068 --> 01:10.200
Hey, guys,
before Anu gets here,

01:10.244 --> 01:12.811
can I talk about
the seating situation?

01:12.855 --> 01:14.509
