to sit on the floor.

01:14.552 --> 01:17.207
Oh. No problem.
Bernadette, floor.

01:17.251 --> 01:19.296
Hey!
Yeah, you can't
make my wife

01:19.340 --> 01:20.863
sit on the floor.Fine.

01:20.906 --> 01:22.908
