01:42.189 --> 01:45.366
All right. Let's
keep thinking.

01:45.409 --> 01:47.498
Hey, everybody, it's Anu.

01:47.542 --> 01:49.065
Hi.

01:49.109 --> 01:50.458
ALL:
Hi! Welcome!

